description: A red sandstone quay, which dates from before the 18th Century, is uncovered by construction workers.
title: Peel stone quay unearthed during pipe replacement work
title_page: Peel stone quay unearthed during pipe replacement work - BBC News
maintext: He added that more finds could be made as part of the pipe replacement work, as the project was due to take in the route of an old railway line, which took supplies to the Knockaloe internment camp in World War One.
